			<tr>
				<td><img src="/img/shorten.png"><br>
				<span>SHORTEN</span><br>
				Shorten, brand and optimize your links across devices and channels. Share them via Bitly, API or partner integrations.
				</td>
				<td><img src="/img/measure.png"><br>
				<span>MEASURE</span><br>
